Package org.fluentlenium.core.events.annotations

Annotation Interface AfterSwitchToWindow

@Target(METHOD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface AfterSwitchToWindow
Add this annotation on a method to register it in EventsRegistry.

Can be used in test adapter and component.

Parameters from SwitchToWindowListener will be injected in the method based on parameters types.

See Also:
  • EventsRegistry.afterSwitchToWindow(org.fluentlenium.core.events.SwitchToWindowListener)
